earings.name: JF Earing - 1
earings.description: Earrings are hypoallergenic as they all have S925 silver pins. Items are made of gold vermeil and S925 silver pin. Designs last upto 6 months before they change their color, it could last up to more than a year with proper care.
earings.material: gold vermeil and S925 silver pin
